1
00:00:14,160 --> 00:00:17,800
The legendary search
for the next top models and actors

2
00:00:17,880 --> 00:00:21,440
that reshaped the Thai entertainment
and fashion industries is back.

3
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:25,680
Join me, Kim Goodburn,
on this historic new journey.

4
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:28,600
This is <i>The Face Men Thailand Season 4</i>.

5
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:38,440
<i>Last week, Team Off proved their team's</i>
<i>worth and crushed the other teams again.</i>

6
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:40,000
Mentor Off's team.

7
00:00:43,480 --> 00:00:46,440
<i>Forcing Team Mile</i>
<i>to send Leo to the Black Room.</i>

8
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:48,240
<i>Meanwhile, Team Pancake-Ananda</i>

9
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:52,280
<i>sent both Lincoln and Donut</i>
<i>to fight together.</i>

10
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:55,680
I will try my absolute best with my Thai.

11
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:58,160
- You might need to practice a little more.
- Yes.

12
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,880
Ananda didn't save my boy.

13
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:02,240
Pan didn't save my boy either.

14
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,400
You remember that?

15
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:05,840
Please, give me a chance.

16
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:09,160
Both Lincoln and Donut…

17
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:10,960
Neither of you is The Face.

18
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:13,120
Leo, you're not The Face either.

19
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:17,800
<i>Mentor Off eliminated</i>
<i>all three contestants</i>

20
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:20,640
<i>in the final Black Room of the season.</i>

21
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:53,680
<i>The winner of </i>The Face Men
Thailand Season 4

22
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,960
<i>will collaborate with Clear Thailand.</i>

23
00:01:56,040 --> 00:02:00,600
<i>He will receive a one-year supply</i>
<i>of Clear Ice Cool Menthol,</i>

24
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:03,160
<i>and the opportunity to work</i>
<i>with Vaseline Thailand.</i>

25
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:06,800
<i>Plus, he'll receive</i>
<i>Vaseline SPF50+ PA++++,</i>

26
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:10,160
<i>Gluta Hyaluronic Acid,</i>
<i>Photoage Defense UV Serum</i>

27
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,000
<i>free for an entire year.</i>

28
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:14,280
<i>He will also collaborate with AXE,</i>

29
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:17,480
<i>and receive a year's supply</i>
<i>of personal care products.</i>

30
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:20,960
<i>Bearbeary, only the wearers feel it.</i>

31
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:24,840
<i>Premium wear for every style,</i>
<i>featuring top design and innovation.</i>

32
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:27,080
<i>They'll award a 100,000-baht gift voucher.</i>

33
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:31,320
<i>Strive for perfection</i>
<i>with a membership to Hotman Fitness.</i>

34
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:34,040
<i>Including an 18-month</i>
<i>personal training program.</i>

35
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:38,040
<i>Plus a 200,000-baht package</i>
<i>from V Design Clinic.</i>

36
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:40,640
<i>Get ready to step onto the national screen</i>

37
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:43,680
<i>through a collaboration</i>
<i>with Channel 3 HD, Thailand.</i>

38
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:47,840
<i>And sign an acting contract</i>
<i>with Kantana Group Public Company Limited,</i>

39
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:50,360
<i>Thailand's leading producer</i>
<i>of dramas and films.</i>

40
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:22,840
- Hello, everyone.
- Hello.

41
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:28,280
We've finally made it to the last
master class of the season.

42
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:32,480
The final master class.
We actually made it here.

43
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:36,680
Just let go and vibe with it.

44
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:40,720
All right, let's dive into the main
challenge of today's master class.

45
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:44,600
Today, two mentors will join us
to give you their expert advice

46
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,920
during the master class challenge.

47
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,840
Please welcome Mentor Mile and Mentor Off.

48
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:56,400
- Hello.
- Hi.

49
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,600
The mentors aren't even teaching today.

50
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:01,400
Straight into the task.
They must be confident in us.

51
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:05,160
So, let's invite the person
giving us today's challenge.

52
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:09,640
Please welcome
Nalinrat Boonnikornvoravith or Jean,

53
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:12,960
Brand Manager for Clear Thailand.

54
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:22,560
NALINRAT BOONNIKORNVORAVITH,
BRAND MANAGER FOR CLEAR THAILAND

55
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,600
All right, Jean.

56
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:26,120
What's the brief for today's master class?

57
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:29,720
Today's challenge is "Up, Up, Clear Away."

58
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:32,600
You guys will be creating
a masterpiece for Clear

59
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:36,160
by starring in a full-scale music video.

60
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:38,840
The key to nailing a music video

61
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:41,200
is radiating total confidence and fun,

62
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:44,680
and bringing out your ultimate charm.

63
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:48,920
We're turning this entire episode
into music content.

64
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,280
And the special twist today?

65
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:54,680
Clear produced a brand new track
called "Is that CLEAR?"

66
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:59,920
It's an exclusive original song
just for <i>The Face Men Season 4.</i>

67
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:07,640
I didn't expect a modeling show to have us
lip-syncing to an original song.

68
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,800
We even got our own song. We get to dance.

69
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,800
The whole package.

70
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:15,120
"I'm clear, clear, clear.
When will you clear it up?"

71
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:18,400
Welcome to <i>The Face Men</i>, Amazing Thailand.

72
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:20,800
We literally got everything here.

73
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:24,000
So, what's the process
for shooting the MV today?

74
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:26,880
We have a very special test,

75
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:29,920
which is designed just for this episode.

76
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:34,280
In the master class, we'll shoot vocals.
The campaign will be the dance lines.

77
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:38,960
Then we'll edit both parts together
to create the perfect, complete video.

78
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:43,440
The lyrics tell the story
of a complicated situationship.

79
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:45,480
The girl won't give the guy a label.

80
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:49,240
So our leading man wants
to clear the air with confidence.

81
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:53,040
This MV follows seven guys

82
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,800
living together
in a floating balloon house.

83
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:58,200
One of them is getting ready to meet

84
00:05:58,280 --> 00:06:01,000
someone special
to keep the spark after the first date.

85
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:04,840
So he kicks off the morning
by serving a killer look,

86
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:07,560
fresh, confident, and dandruff-free,

87
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:10,080
before heading out
to clear the air with his date.

88
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:12,640
Big thanks to Clear

89
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:15,880
for giving this kid
the opportunity to try something new.

90
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,360
I love you, Clear.

91
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:19,280
Why does it have to be Clear shampoo?

92
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:21,680
Because Clear Ice Cool Menthol

93
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:24,280
is the ultimate fix
for an active lifestyle.

94
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:28,000
No matter how many challenges
or stress you face,

95
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:30,520
it helps you stay clean, fresh,

96
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:34,800
refreshed, dandruff-free,
and confident all day.

97
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:39,160
What exactly are you expecting
from the boys in today's master class?

98
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,320
I want to see your vibe.

99
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:44,320
The confident vibe of a Clear Man.

100
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:47,320
Fun, cool, and a little cheeky.

101
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:49,520
Most importantly, confidence is the key

102
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:52,000
before you go out and make things clear.

103
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:53,560
Besides confidence, have fun.

104
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,360
Just be yourself.

105
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:58,720
Interpret it through your own feelings.

106
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:02,360
You will find your own unique character
and charisma within.

107
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:05,880
Most importantly, remember how
you present your emotions.

108
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:07,280
You have to truly feel it.

109
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,920
Be yourself all the way. Don't force it.

110
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,160
That's when your true charm shines.

111
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,320
That's my advice.

112
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:15,280
Today's master class isn't too hard.

113
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:18,440
For our team, music campaigns are easy.

114
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:21,720
The same goes for this master class.
If there's music, it's easy.

115
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,640
All right,

116
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:26,880
let me explain the rules
for today's master class.

117
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:30,400
Today, everyone will star
in a full music video.

118
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,160
There will be solo segments

119
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:35,240
and parts where your teammates join in.

120
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:37,440
For your singing parts,

121
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:41,360
you must lip-sync perfectly.

122
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:45,600
Beyond that, feel free to get creative.

123
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:50,400
Each of you gets only one take
to shoot the MV.

124
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,880
The one who stands out the most

125
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,800
will win today's master class.

126
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,160
And for today,

127
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:58,760
we have two guest judges

128
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:01,800
joining us for this master class.

129
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:02,800
First up,

130
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:05,720
Thailand's very first <i>The Face </i>winner,

131
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,040
Sabina.

132
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,760
- Hello.
- Hello.

133
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:16,920
Sabina is so gorgeous.

134
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:19,640
Kim and I just nudged
each other, fanboying.

135
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:22,560
Another judge…

136
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,760
is a talented singer and actor.

137
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,920
Please welcome, Ice Paris.

138
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:34,919
- Hello.
- Hello.

139
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,679
His vocals are flawless.

140
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,600
His acting is top-notch.

141
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:41,600
He's the perfect judge for today.

142
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:44,880
Today's master class is an MV shoot,

143
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,520
with vocal lines.

144
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,240
Any advice for the guys?

145
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:51,440
First off, memorize those lyrics.

146
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,040
That's crucial in my opinion.

147
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:57,160
The brief asks for emotion and confidence.

148
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:59,520
And you can only show that
when you're relaxed.

149
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:02,000
So I hope you practice hard.

150
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,280
Give it your all, and it will show.

151
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:10,840
I'm ready to rock. Are you guys ready?

152
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:15,240
If you're ready, go prepare
for the "Up, Up, Clear Away" master class.

153
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:20,480
I feel like I'm carrying the team's hopes.

154
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:24,200
I'm ready to step up for everyone.

155
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:26,560
Ready to let loose.
I'm here to have fun today.

156
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:39,680
Welcome back to today's master class.
Today's brief is "Up, Up, Clear Away."

157
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:42,160
Today, you'll be shooting a music video,

158
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:44,200
lip-syncing to "Is that CLEAR?"

159
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:47,080
while looking active,
fresh, and well-groomed

160
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:48,920
like a true Clear Man.

161
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,320
And now, our contestants are ready.

162
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:53,640
Let's welcome our first model.

163
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,920
Manyoo, step up, please.

164
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:01,800
It's a huge disadvantage
to perform before everyone else.

165
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:04,120
But it's fine. I'll just let loose.

166
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,280
Ready? Action.

167
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:23,000
Manyoo isn't exactly a dancer.

168
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:26,800
But he enjoys the music.
Let's see what he's got.

169
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:36,400
His entrance was actually pretty good,

170
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:40,600
but once the music started,
he looked a bit tense.

171
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:41,760
Just a little.

172
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,080
Yes, a little.

173
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:45,960
I can't dance at all.
I have zero body control.

174
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:49,040
This is just totally not my vibe.

175
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:51,400
- Oh, here they come.
- Move over a little.

176
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,920
Will he be upstaged?

177
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:56,720
The main issue is that
his lip-syncing is off.

178
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:59,000
When it's off,
it ruins the whole vocal vibe.

179
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:05,680
What I disliked most

180
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:08,160
was how stiff his face looked.
During the lip-sync…

181
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,640
his insecurity really showed.

182
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:16,000
It wasn't bad. It was fine.
I think I did well in my own way.

183
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:19,320
That's it for our first contestant.
Next, Kimhan.

184
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,000
Let's go.

185
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,960
I'm totally fired up today.

186
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:26,880
If I were a car, my tank would be full.

187
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,840
I'm so ready to crush the competition.

188
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:36,240
- Great opening.
- He's telling a story.

189
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:44,080
Three minutes felt so long at first.
When it started, it flew right by.

190
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,240
I didn't plan a thing.

191
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:48,520
I just acted like it was my own song.

192
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:53,120
When he looks at the camera,
he looks good.

193
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,280
It feels so alive.

194
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,920
There isn't a dull moment.

195
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:58,480
- Creative opening, consistent energy.
- Right.

196
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:00,280
Oh, a spin.

197
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:07,400
My favorite part? His eye contact.

198
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:12,160
He says so much with his eyes and poses.

199
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:14,120
Smart and smooth transitions.

200
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:24,320
Total mob boss energy.

201
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:30,320
Kimhan is too good.

202
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:32,480
Honestly, I couldn't take my eyes off him.

203
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,440
Next up, Gluf.

204
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:37,080
Piercing the camera. Serving face.

205
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,680
Acting his age. Very youthful.

206
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:55,440
Yes, super youthful.

207
00:12:56,560 --> 00:13:00,120
Gluf's youth really comes through
on camera.

208
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,720
At first, he was smoldering.

209
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:08,040
Then his playful, boyish charm came out.

210
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,040
His acting was great.

211
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:17,480
He had amazing facial expressions.

212
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:18,480
I just let loose.

213
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:21,960
I think in the final cut, everyone's vibe

214
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:24,600
and my performance
will come together perfectly.

215
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:26,120
It's so good.

216
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:30,920
We really came together today.

217
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,480
Total harmony and teamwork.

218
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:35,640
The seven of us could debut as a boy band.

219
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:44,080
Slayed that ending.

220
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:47,000
He's a hard seller. Total hard seller.

221
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:50,200
He doesn't care about the balance
or hitting the perfect pose.

222
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:52,040
Just, "I'm selling this. Bam."

223
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,440
He's all about the KPIs.

224
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:56,120
At least Gluf hit his KPIs.

225
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:58,240
Let's bring out our next guy.

226
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,520
Welcome, Bonus.

227
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,440
Hello.

228
00:14:03,520 --> 00:14:05,680
Ready right out the gate.

229
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:07,520
Zero concentration is needed for this.

230
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,840
It's all in my hips.

231
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:20,440
This show definitely needs a guy like him.

232
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:22,640
We needed a dancer like this.

233
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:25,160
His nickname is TT-Pop.

234
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:27,240
True Thai Pop.

235
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:32,280
Don't drop the product.

236
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,880
Never drop the product.

237
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:38,200
I accidentally knocked over
the Clear bottle. I was like, "Oh, crap."

238
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:41,720
The product display got a bit messy.
But I recovered and gave it my all.

239
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:51,040
Okay.

240
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:54,960
I saw him doing that little hip roll.

241
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,200
He just wouldn't stop.

242
00:14:56,280 --> 00:15:00,440
I was like, "Bonus,
are you doing this the whole time?"

243
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:02,680
That's his selling point.

244
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,360
The hips.

245
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:10,800
Everyone absolutely loved watching Bonus.

246
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:12,400
Even I enjoyed it.

247
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,800
It was so much fun.

248
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:17,200
He's just a fun guy. Loved it.

249
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:32,040
I don't know what he achieved,
but we had fun.

250
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:36,360
