but they probably loved me.

251
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:38,800
Overall, it was fabulous.

252
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,280
Just fab, fab.

253
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:44,040
Let's move on to our next guy, Pom.

254
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:48,200
- Come on.
- Okay.

255
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:50,680
