283
00:18:11,560 --> 00:18:13,160
Rome's little "meow."

284
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,800
Bonus points for the "meow."

285
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:16,360
Meow.

286
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:17,520
Slay, slay, slay.

287
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:18,640
It worked, though.

288
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:21,560
That's exactly how people remember you.

289
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:24,600
