294
00:18:33,520 --> 00:18:35,080
Hey, that's creative.

295
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:36,760
Unique opening.

296
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:42,240
- That body pop? Sick.
- Yes.

297
00:18:42,320 --> 00:18:44,000
Slay, slay, slay.

298
00:18:48,360 --> 00:18:50,040
He's packed with energy.

299
00:18:50,120 --> 00:18:53,280
Even in the back,
he was giving it his all.

300
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:55,320
So energetic and fun to watch.

301
00:18:58,280 --> 00:19:00,040
He knows how to move.

302
00:19:00,120 --> 00:19:00,960
Hold on.

303
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:04,440
He's got charm, and he can dance and move.

304
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:07,040
Today, I just let loose.

305
00:19:07,120 --> 00:19:10,400
I gave my all and did something different.
I gave it my everything.

306
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:20,280
I loved the rap part.
His rapper vibe is so on point.

307
00:19:20,360 --> 00:19:22,200
And super smooth.

308
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:25,080
- Nice opening. So creative.
- Yes.

309
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:41,120
This was truly his master class.

310
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:43,760
He's in his element
when it comes to dancing and singing.

311
00:19:43,840 --> 00:19:45,920
From the second Peem walked in,

312
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:49,160
