Right down to the last second.

313
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:50,480
He did everything right.

314
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:54,640
I have absolutely zero notes for Peem.
He's definitely a frontrunner. No doubt.

315
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:06,520
Oh, hey.

316
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:08,000
Yes, wow.

317
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:15,160
- How was that?
- Amazing job, Peem.

318
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:19,760
What I loved most
was how he balanced his energy.

319
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:21,280
It wasn't too over the top.

320
00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:23,680
It was just perfect. Really, really good.

321
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:26,160
I had the highest hopes
for Peem this episode.

322
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:28,480
This had to be his day, man.

323
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:30,280
Just now, our contestants

324
00:20:30,360 --> 00:20:33,240
showed us what it means to be a Clear Man.

325
00:20:33,320 --> 00:20:36,640
Now, let's hear
what the judges have to say.

326
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:39,360
How did everyone do
overall in this master class?

327
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:41,800
I have to say, everyone did a great job.

328
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:44,400
You all managed to bring agility

329
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:47,040
and incredible energy to the set.

330
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:51,840
Your opening and closing designs
were all very strong.

331
00:20:51,920 --> 00:20:53,560
I commend you all.

332
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:55,840
You are seven incredibly talented guys.

333
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,840
We are all so impressed.

334
00:20:57,920 --> 00:21:01,240
Be proud of how far you've come.
Excellent work.

335
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:05,960
The one thing that stood out
was how memorable you all were.

336
00:21:06,040 --> 00:21:09,520
Everyone brought their own unique flavor,
beyond my expectations, truly.

337
00:21:09,600 --> 00:21:12,040
That is phenomenal.
A round of applause for you all.

338
00:21:12,120 --> 00:21:14,840
I loved seeing
how much fun you guys were having.

339
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:17,880
Your individual characters
shone through that joy.

340
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:20,240
I'm happy with the results.

341
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:23,200
Great job, everyone.

342
00:21:23,280 --> 00:21:26,000
You all showed intent and a clear vision

343
00:21:26,080 --> 00:21:28,760
