is totally different.

344
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:30,600
It's all open to interpretation,

345
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:33,320
and you all stayed true to yourselves.

346
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:38,720
This was the most joyful master class yet.

347
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:41,760
Not just for me, but for everyone.
All seven of us.

348
00:21:41,840 --> 00:21:45,120
We're all thrilled. It was heartwarming.

349
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,440
Like a big family.

350
00:21:46,520 --> 00:21:49,200
Everyone is happy. Super wholesome vibes.

351
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:51,640
Now, we will announce the top three

352
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:54,680
