in today's master class.

353
00:21:54,760 --> 00:21:57,200
Jean, who are our top three?

354
00:21:57,280 --> 00:22:01,320
I have to say, this took some time.
It was a really tough decision.

355
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:06,840
But someone has to come out on top, right?

356
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:11,240
The three models we've selected are…

357
00:22:11,320 --> 00:22:12,160
Kimhan.

358
00:22:15,120 --> 00:22:17,000
Pom.

359
00:22:17,080 --> 00:22:18,920
We're back at the top again.

360
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,360
- We meet again.
- Keep it up.

361
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:22,400
And Peem.

362
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:26,280
I'm crashing the top this time.
Joining your squad today.

363
00:22:26,360 --> 00:22:28,560
You were all incredibly evenly matched.

364
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:30,560
You each have such standout styles.

365
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:32,880
Starting with Peem,

366
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:36,560
you had a very clear vision
for your composition.

367
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:43,120
Your choices of props were outstanding.
You used the props really well.

368
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:46,000
It didn't feel too much.

369
00:22:46,080 --> 00:22:49,320
During your rapper part,
your character was crystal clear.

370
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:53,960
And that opening. I'm impressed
that you chose the headphones.

371
00:22:54,040 --> 00:22:57,680
It gave it a really cool music video vibe.

372
00:22:57,760 --> 00:22:59,080
Next up, Pom.

373
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:01,400
Great opening. So smooth.

374
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:05,240
Your movements were flawless. Loved it.
You were completely in your element.

375
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:08,720
Kimhan, you are such a strong contender.

376
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:12,280
You always bring that "wow" factor.
I'm impressed.

377
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:14,920
It's genuinely hard to find any flaws.

378
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:15,840
Superb work.

379
00:23:17,320 --> 00:23:19,080
Be proud of yourself.

380
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:20,600
Thank you.

381
00:23:22,520 --> 00:23:24,920
All right, before we reveal
the final results,

382
00:23:25,000 --> 00:23:27,440
I heard there's a special prize,
